
## Installation instructions

The app can be accessed with the following URL : [https://pinich.github.io/AZLite](https://pinich.github.io/AZLite)

## Using installation script
Execute `./scripts/installation.sh` file.
## Manual installation
#### Step 1
```bash
cd client && npm i
```
#### Step 2
To start the server with static client run `npm run start` from server directory

## Deployment
To deploy the app to Github-Pages run the following command from client directory:
```bash
npm run deploy
```